OL,3,CMore people turning to medical
OL,4,Ccannabis to help with health conditions
OL,6,FCannabis, a classified B drug in the
OL,7,FUK, remains the focus of significant
OL,8,Fpolice time and resource. However,
OL,9,Fthere are growing calls for laws
OL,10,Faround its use to be updated, with
OL,11,Fsome arguing it should be legalised
OL,12,Fcompletely.
OL,14,FAt a cannabis lounge in Newport there
OL,15,Fis a key distinction- everyone using
OL,16,Fthe drug on the premises holds a
OL,17,Fprivate medical prescription.
