OL,3,CMore people turning to medical
OL,4,Ccannabis to help with health conditions
OL,6,FMedical cannabis was legalised in the
OL,7,FUK in 2018. This means that a
OL,8,Fspecialist private doctor can
OL,9,Fprescribe cannabis for a range of
OL,10,Fconditions (including chronic pain,
OL,11,Fanxiety, and MS), provided the patient
OL,12,Fhas already tried two conventional
OL,13,Ftreatments without success.
OL,15,FThe customers inside the lounge
OL,16,Frepresent a growing community in the
OL,17,FUK, who use cannabis legally under a
OL,18,Fmedical prescription.
