OL,3,CMore people turning to medical
OL,4,Ccannabis to help with health conditions
OL,6,FChantelle detailed her struggle to
OL,7,Ffind effective help through
OL,8,Fconventional medicine:
OL,10,FShe said: "I wasn't able to get the
OL,11,Fcorrect medication I need for certain
OL,12,Fconditions that I have, so I've tried
OL,13,Fso many different ones... I had to
OL,14,Ffind something else to use and I feel
OL,15,Flike I've found something that helps
OL,16,Fmassively."
