OL,3,CMore people turning to medical
OL,4,Ccannabis to help with health conditions
OL,6,FWhen asked about the potential for
OL,7,Fpeople to fake conditions to get
OL,8,Fprescriptions, Chantelle said that
OL,9,Fabuse exists across all types of
OL,10,Fmedicine.
OL,12,F"I feel like that happens in all sorts
OL,13,Fof medicine though, like people go to
OL,14,Fthe doctors and play up like they need
OL,15,Fsleeping pills or whatever just to
OL,16,Fabuse them, so I feel like you'll find
OL,17,Fthat in any sort of industry where
OL,18,Fthey're prescribing medication."
