OL,3,CMore people turning to medical
OL,4,Ccannabis to help with health conditions
OL,6,FHowever, one drug charity has concerns
OL,7,Fthat not everyone can afford to access
OL,8,Fthe drug through a private cannabis
OL,9,Fclinic.
OL,11,FThe Chief Executive Officer of
OL,12,FKaleidoscope, Rondine Molinaro, said
OL,13,Fshe felt 'uneasy' that some members of
OL,14,Fsociety would be priced out of being
OL,15,Fable access the medication, which
OL,16,Fcould lead to criminalisation.
