OL,6,FShe said: "what about the people that
OL,7,Fdon't have the means to go and get a
OL,8,Fprivate prescription? So they are
OL,9,Fstill going to be criminalised. So in
OL,10,Fa way, it's a little bit of a war on
OL,11,Fthe poor?"
OL,13,FCannabis is the most commonly used
OL,14,Fillegal drug in the UK and has
OL,15,Fconsistently accounted for the
OL,16,Fmajority of drug seizures.
OL,18,FIn the year ending March 2024 there
OL,19,Fwere 152,000 seizures of cannabis, and
OL,20,Fincrease from the previous year
OL,21,F(140,363).
