OL,3,CMore people turning to medical
OL,4,Ccannabis to help with health conditions
OL,6,FITV Wales followed North Wales Police
OL,7,Fon a warrant at a property in Bangor,
OL,8,Fwhere officers discovered an estimated
OL,9,F#6,000 worth of cannabis.
OL,11,FIt was just one of the numerous raids
OL,12,FNorth Wales Police conduct each year
OL,13,Fas part of their strategy to tackle
OL,14,Fthe use and supply of drugs.
OL,16,FWhen asked about whether cannabis
OL,17,Fshould be legalised completely, the
OL,18,FPolice and Crime Commissioner for
OL,19,FDyfed Powys, Dafydd Llewellyn said
OL,20,Fdespite the law being 'somewhat dated'
OL,21,Fthe issue remains complicated.
