OL,3,CMore people turning to medical
OL,4,Ccannabis to help with health conditions
OL,6,FHe said: "What we have found, is that
OL,7,Fwithin the cultivations we have in
OL,8,FDyfed Powys area, the potent level of
OL,9,Fthe cannabis that we have - the skunk
OL,10,Fcannabis being produced and then sold
OL,11,Fillicitly across the force area, that
OL,12,FI would say is a worry, we don't know
OL,13,Fthe impact of that.
OL,15,F"Decriminalisation has worked in
OL,16,Fplaces like Portugal, it's worked well
OL,17,Fin Switzerland, but what about the
OL,18,Fareas where there's been a full
OL,19,Flegalisation, has that worked? I'm a
OL,20,Fbit skeptical if I'm honest."
